      "content": "it just feels so much easier to just handle it at home. honestly i've noticed that if i just sit down and do some deep breathing exercises like i saw online, it helps clear the heaviness a bit. i'm thinking if i just double up on my regular dose for a few days i can probably just get through this patch without having to deal with the clinic. it's probably just my lungs getting a bit weaker with age, right? it's not usually this serious, so it's fine to just push through it for a week or so?",
